    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录最繁忙的一天，各大公司纷纷涌入债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/corporations-stampede-into-bond-market-in-busiest-day-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二上午，创纪录数量的蓝筹公司涌入公司债券市场，利用较低的借贷成本，在美国总统大选前发行债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/corporations-stampede-into-bond-market-in-busiest-day-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>住宅太阳能公司 Lumio 申请破产，计划出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/residential-solar-firm-lumio-files-bankruptcy-plans-to-sell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lumio 是一家私营住宅太阳能电池板供应商，该公司申请破产，计划将其业务出售给主要贷方 White Oak Global Advisors LLC。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/residential-solar-firm-lumio-files-bankruptcy-plans-to-sell</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛将铜价预测下调 5,000 美元，看涨押注已结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-slashes-copper-forecast-on-softening-chinese-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 退出了对铜的长期看涨头寸，并将 2025 年铜价预测下调近 5,000 美元，理由是中国需求萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-slashes-copper-forecast-on-softening-chinese-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
